      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION ¶ FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON. ¶ J. G. Otto Tepper Esqr ¶ of Adelaide ¶ a gentleman attached to the study of Natural History, especially ¶  entomology...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">79.08.00</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To the Linnean Society of London</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Linnean Society, London, Certificates of Fellows, Foreign Members and Associates, 1877-82.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FORM OF RECOMMENDATION</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">FOR A FELLOW OF THE LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">J. G. Otto Tepper Esqr</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">of Adelaide</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">a gentleman attached to the study of Natural History, especially</seg>
               </seg> entomology</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">being desirous of becoming a Fellow of the LINNEAN SOCIETY OF LONDON, we, whose names are underwritten, beg leave to recommend him to that honour.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-align: end; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Ferd. von Mueller, M.D., PhD, FLS<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Tepper’s details completed and form signed by M; other supporters' autograph signatures. It is not known when the form was signed by Woolls and Fitzgerald; the document is dated to August 1879 by reference to M to O. Tepper, 10 August 1879.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-align: end; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">William Woolls Ph.D., F.L.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0in; margin-right: 0.9402in; text-align: end; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Robt D FitzGerald F.L.S</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">
                  <seg style="font-style: italic; ">This recommendation must be signed by Three or more Fellows.</seg>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">N.B. – The Christian name of the Candidate must be stated at length, as well as his Residence, and any special qualifications he may possess.</seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">This certificate was read at a General Meeting of the Society, on the</seg> 6th <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg> November 1879.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">The Ballot will take place on the </seg>4 <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">day of</seg> December 1879.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Annotated on front</seg>: Elected, Rd. K.</p>
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg style="font-style: italic; ">On back</seg>: J G Otto Tepper Esq <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Adelaide <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Elected Dec 4, 1879</p>
                  <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
               </note>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
